Prospectuses & SupplementsLow, easy-to-understand pricing.With the Schwab Retirement Income Variable Annuity®, you’ll have the satisfaction of knowing that the annuity fees you pay fall well below the industry average. 
You know exactly what you’re paying—fees are straightforward and fully disclosed. 
You pay less than half the average base variable annuity fee charged in the industry.2
There are no surrender charges or surrender periods if you decide to withdraw your money for any reason.3
You can fund your annuity with a minimum investment of  $50,000.  

