How much can you save? Already own a variable annuity elsewhere? See how much you might save by exchanging your current variable annuity for a low-cost annuity at Schwab. Before exchanging your current annuity, you should consider a number of important factors that could reduce or eliminate the benefit of the exchange. These include surrender charges on your existing contract, loss of guaranteed benefits, and differences in features, costs, services, and company strength.
