About the Schwab Retirement Income Variable Annuity®
The Schwab Retirement Income Variable Annuity is a variable annuity with an optional Guaranteed Lifetime Withdrawal Benefit rider and two death benefit options each available for an additional cost. It seeks to provide tax-deferred growth, a range of diversified investment portfolios, and guaranteed income for life1.






